# Planning documents

When producing **implementation plans**, **design notes**, or **structured planning markdown** meant to live in this repository, write them under **`.dev/plans/`** (unless the user specifies another path).

Do not recreate a top-level `docs/` tree for this purpose unless the user asks.

When a plan introduces **new planned work**, ensure corresponding **Linear issues** exist (or create them) and link `TOR-*` ids in [RUNNING TASKLIST](../../.dev/RUNNING%20TASKLIST.md). See `.cursor/rules/toronto-rising-linear.mdc`.
